snippet.title: EERIE MOUNTAIN - OFFICIAL GAMEPLAY TRAILER
snippet.description:
There is a missing family on the Eerie Mountain do you dare to go and try to find them?


Hello everyone! 
this is a new horror game of mine that i have been working on for quite some time now, would be appreciated if you give it a go and let me know how it goes!
Download it here from my itch.io:
https://korvinrular.itch.io/eerie-mountain
